# 1.5 Customer Enablement & Schema Explanation

This section describes how customers were enabled to **understand and self-serve data**.

---

## Tools Supported
- Answers (SQL-based analytics interface)
- Excel Add-in reporting tools

---

## Responsibilities
- Explained database schemas in business language
- Guided customers on:
  - Dimensions
  - Product hierarchies
  - KPI definitions
- Helped customers interpret outputs correctly

---

## Outcome
Customers were able to:
- Navigate the database confidently
- Build or adjust reports independently
- Trust the analytical results

This reduced operational dependency and improved customer satisfaction.
